改服务工作的通知》，针对国内出现局部聚集性疫情的地区，要求各航空公司及时制定发布客票免费退改方案，并加强信息告知和宣传。通知下发后，国内各航空公司及时跟进发布了具体实施方案。民航局于今日下发的通知，旨在响应 1 月 25 日中共中央办公厅、国务院办公厅下发的《关于做好人民群众就地过年服务保障工作的通知》，进一步扩大了免费退改政策的适用范围，落实春节假期非必要不流动的号召。（来源：新华社）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8188c93e9d3e43e8e7d4d463b5dddfcf_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "140 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441269193"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/6bH0tvq0YBZEAMaCDYwMzM3OTE4IJDmvoAGMAM4rQJAE3IJNDQxMjY5MTkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1611714262.1625364", "card_id": "Q_440997091", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 52}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待小米在 3000 档甚至 2000 档空位？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "小米手机 2000 档现在除了小米 10 青春版外，只剩下半卖半不卖的红米 K30 至尊 /K30S 至尊，红米 K30 Pro 降价前价格被限制在 3000 元以下，红米 K30Pro 变焦版没卖出多少，小米 10 降价前也将近 4000 元。 对比 HOV，2500-4000 是主力布局的价位，从出货量上非旗舰机可比，单机利润上非千元机可比，Nova/Reno/Vivos/x/ 荣耀 V/ 数字都在该价位大力布局。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-0407d4cc1db7797ea21ef703631da3a7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "139 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/440997091"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/6bH0tvq0YBZEAMaCDYwMjc3MzkxIM3otYAGMAU44AFAFHIJNDQwOTk3MDkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1611714262.1630967", "card_id": "Q_441218199", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 187}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待番茄小说后台曝光，被发现私吞作者稿费?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a88f439aa677e770e7df9754b9e63e63_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "129 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441218199"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/6bH0